{
  "title": "Infecciones del SNC",
  "guid": "2A40090C028F027715570715",
  "filepath": "/sessions/bold-jolly-cerf/mnt/Dropbox/- Esquemas/- Entidades clínicas/Infectología/MKSAP 18. Infecciones del SNC-2025-1.smmx",
  "root": {
    "id": "0",
    "parent": "-1",
    "text": "Infecciones del SNC",
    "guid": "RGtcd1McOaFviziOU15c0Q",
    "children": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "### Meningitis",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "2",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "- Meningitis\nviral",
            "guid": "Y5EmAiG92Rs5r2dZKYK1qw",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "3",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "- Causa más común: enterovirus",
                "guid": "aENExkDfc_Btx-y-ReEZig",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "4",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "- Presentación típica: entre mayo y noviembre en hemisferio norte occidental",
                "guid": "b2OFexyRRP0kIcPIOmPDfw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "5",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "- Síntomas: cefalea, fiebre, rigidez de nuca, fotofobia, náuseas, vómitos, mialgias, faringitis, exantema maculopapular, tos",
                "guid": "KoWAaWLEVQFzkS6qFAhbxg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "6",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "- Diagnóstico: PCR para enterovirus",
                "guid": "DQReDnYgMSEpX2LbUW-6hQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "7",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "- Tratamiento: medidas de apoyo",
                "guid": "STxqwxjqm2kkzhdWGOgNiQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "8",
                "parent": "2",
                "text": "- Agentes causales:",
                "guid": "C4RDxD-8e8tLFWWCKBrlNQ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "9",
                    "parent": "8",
                    "text": "- Herpesvirus: pueden causar\nmeningitis durante todo el año",
                    "guid": "cH3c1jGcPj8Qy0laVA8C2A",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "10",
                        "parent": "9",
                        "text": "- VHS tipo 2: más frecuente, puede recurrir",
                        "guid": "U1oXWkp6sLN9kbiDO51cIQ",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "11",
                        "parent": "9",
                        "text": "- VVZ (virus varicela-zóster)",
                        "guid": "C1oko2tZpUIBfnWrer2qHg",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "12",
                        "parent": "9",
                        "text": "- Virus de Epstein-Barr",
                        "guid": "B-rqPyWgOXQ1IW2dMnBqqA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "13",
                        "parent": "9",
                        "text": "- Herpesvirus humano 6",
                        "guid": "CGSOdSiynEhGeMZuFWjsgw",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "14",
                    "parent": "8",
                    "text": "- Hallazgos en LCR: similares a meningitis enteroviral",
                    "guid": "HtLNaW_YKUlm2KcIaA84LA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "15",
                    "parent": "8",
                    "text": "- Evolución VHS-2: favorable sin terapia con aciclovir",
                    "guid": "CMLEsgumvl8A90W1FEcIdw",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "16",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "- Meningitis\nbacteriana",
            "guid": "S2M6KkwMqzc8Ye2sO-EXAA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "17",
                "parent": "16",
                "text": "- Signos meníngeos agudos + alteración del estado mental",
                "guid": "fajpdk0tNwYP8BnZUQMA0Q",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "18",
                "parent": "16",
                "text": "- Incidencia disminuida por vacunas contra H. influenzae y N. meningitidis",
                "guid": "F6fnuQ2B0lwMoFzyIwIMXA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "19",
                "parent": "16",
                "text": "- Agentes\nprincipales:",
                "guid": "eNt3ng4e0p0dv7Z6AMZh3g",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "20",
                    "parent": "19",
                    "text": "- S. pneumoniae: causa más frecuente en comunidad",
                    "guid": "M78MEVLhJBczNsyGPCOahw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "21",
                    "parent": "19",
                    "text": "- N. meningitidis: 40% de infecciones en EEUU",
                    "guid": "e5PAX3mvkvVRjIcKGmaNyQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "22",
                    "parent": "19",
                    "text": "- Listeria monocytogenes: mayor riesgo en ancianos/inmunocomprometidos",
                    "guid": "aYe8PjhlLhMCdcX1ckqA8Q",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "23",
                "parent": "16",
                "text": "- Diagnóstico:",
                "guid": "RAvscgNtC6sGkYloD28mnA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "24",
                    "parent": "23",
                    "text": "- Tinción de Gram del LCR: positiva en 60-90%",
                    "guid": "T3m24kLzdxRLUD2cTSKgWQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "25",
                    "parent": "23",
                    "text": "- No se recomiendan pruebas de aglutinación con látex (baja sensibilidad)",
                    "guid": "ECCuGltAV3UeJaEqJ8iV0w",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "26",
                    "parent": "23",
                    "text": "- PCR: alta sensibilidad (100%) y especificidad (98%)",
                    "guid": "aMIp0irF_hxKyqIvYZ2hcA",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "27",
                "parent": "16",
                "text": "- Manejo:",
                "guid": "OOTQuWiKWKliZANObKPcyw",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "28",
                    "parent": "27",
                    "text": "- Tratamiento antibiótico empírico inmediato",
                    "guid": "O2t8wBWaz9Uox3dSNv89IA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "29",
                    "parent": "27",
                    "text": "- Selección basada en edad, patrones epidemiológicos y resistencia local",
                    "guid": "D0piynpT_lxRZcrpeNIfCA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "30",
                    "parent": "27",
                    "text": "- Dexametasona adyuvante: reduce mortalidad y secuelas neurológicas",
                    "guid": "Mrksb1PbkN5rHJ_5dsUY4Q",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "31",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "- Meningitis\nsubaguda y crónica",
        "guid": "V0iciXGuKWEGND99JsJTbA",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "32",
            "parent": "31",
            "text": "- Duración: 5-30 días (subaguda), >30 días (crónica)",
            "guid": "NKGgdVGEfRpz5PPFRMJOjw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "33",
            "parent": "31",
            "text": "- Causas comunes: Mycobacterium tuberculosis y hongos",
            "guid": "LMTUjxIKlO9siuRiFYb-YQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "34",
            "parent": "31",
            "text": "- Meningitis\ntuberculosa",
            "guid": "PNCTCzdVhpF3JJ_SdbVjxA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "35",
                "parent": "34",
                "text": "- Presentación: meningitis basilar, neuropatías craneales, alteraciones mentales",
                "guid": "H9_fOlmIoyBiWUCPW0tb-w",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "36",
                "parent": "34",
                "text": "- Hallazgos: síndrome de secreción inapropiada de hormona antidiurética",
                "guid": "byNy9Qsgt-ESSpkbfm3Vvw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "37",
                "parent": "34",
                "text": "- Diagnóstico: antecedente de exposición, prueba cutánea tuberculina positiva",
                "guid": "BXS2PmOwZAR3P_TIOC3irQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "38",
                "parent": "34",
                "text": "- LCR: pleocitosis linfocítica, nivel elevado de proteínas, hipoglucorraquia",
                "guid": "N4v04mJclMEu8vuPDtSRbA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "39",
                "parent": "34",
                "text": "- Tratamiento: terapia antituberculosa (1 año) + glucocorticoides adyuvantes",
                "guid": "VAq-IzUnOww1luTYCKxemA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "40",
            "parent": "31",
            "text": "- Meningitis\nfúngica",
            "guid": "Bqu4Jil72J1Nbq0oM3CMtg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "41",
                "parent": "40",
                "text": "- Patógenos: Cryptococcus neoformans, Coccidioides immitis, Histoplasma capsulatum",
                "guid": "O4ZtjDn5kYpI94sXeFcAlw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "42",
                "parent": "40",
                "text": "- Más común en inmunocomprometidos",
                "guid": "cU8YHEAcKuluDGRbES73Vg",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "43",
            "parent": "31",
            "text": "- Neurobruscelosis",
            "guid": "GaTOClBlpOtselNRCMhA_w",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "44",
                "parent": "43",
                "text": "- Afecta 4-11% de pacientes con brucelosis",
                "guid": "W4ZczH7E7GwHNha_YPsTCg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "45",
                "parent": "43",
                "text": "- Endémica: Mediterráneo, Oriente Medio, América Central",
                "guid": "YnVQcH52C4cZKPW4GgFFUw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "46",
                "parent": "43",
                "text": "- Tratamiento: antimicrobianos (rifampicina, doxiciclina) mínimo 6 meses",
                "guid": "YNKgSEgb8Uco1da_NN1eaw",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "47",
            "parent": "31",
            "text": "- Meningitis\nparasitaria",
            "guid": "fUMsU15su5c9ib0EA-7keg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "48",
                "parent": "47",
                "text": "- Meningoencefalitis amebiana primaria: Naegleria, Balamuthia, Acanthamoeba",
                "guid": "B-iUNAr4aiw3X3EwQ28BwA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "49",
                "parent": "47",
                "text": "- Exposición a ambientes de agua dulce: indicio histórico clave",
                "guid": "RPH7tgBW_Ec7xgJXNkET0g",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "50",
                "parent": "47",
                "text": "- Tratamiento: miltefosina",
                "guid": "QHMnMSnSZrJHcAspWhf1Ow",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "51",
            "parent": "31",
            "text": "- Causas no infecciosas\nde meningitis",
            "guid": "ejgLnTPqXnpi4DY6Vb5oag",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "52",
                "parent": "51",
                "text": "- Medicamentos: antiinflamatorios, antibióticos, inmunoglobulina",
                "guid": "Mq9K52oWTPk2uXt0FSSbVw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "53",
                "parent": "51",
                "text": "- Otras: carcinoma meníngeo, lupus eritematoso sistémico, enfermedad de Behçet",
                "guid": "aIxYgE_icSwvJeCqSV74yQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "54",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "### Meningitis y ventriculitis\nasociadas a atención sanitaria",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "55",
            "parent": "54",
            "text": "- Causas habituales: Staphylococcus spp. y bacterias gramnegativas",
            "guid": "F_5ic1f7t2l-PFc0FUGOxw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "56",
            "parent": "54",
            "text": "- Factores de riesgo: traumatismo craneoencefálico, procedimientos neuroquirúrgicos",
            "guid": "NmhzADvGFDgZMHNBPlEHNA",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "57",
            "parent": "54",
            "text": "- Diagnóstico: análisis de β-D-glucano y galactomanano en LCR",
            "guid": "Rr5-ZFCP5HEBwAj0C7B6Gw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "58",
            "parent": "54",
            "text": "- Tratamiento: antimicrobiano empírico + retirada del dispositivo implantado",
            "guid": "UObguD2GC0tB8Y3tEVoH6Q",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "59",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "## Infecciones focales del\nsistema nervioso central",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "60",
            "parent": "59",
            "text": "### Abscesos\ncerebrales",
            "guid": "Z1hx_glhmRZrcf0kYZB9mw",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "61",
                "parent": "60",
                "text": "- Afectan principalmente a inmunocomprometidos/inmunodeprimidos",
                "guid": "PUv3kU5SM183TuYFb_tCeA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "62",
                "parent": "60",
                "text": "- Predominio en varones",
                "guid": "OGiAWG4IYXoFH93PIPTY2Q",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "63",
                "parent": "60",
                "text": "- Procesos\npredisponentes\nprincipales:",
                "guid": "QEEEWDi2w3w3LAQ1J5l2Vg",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "64",
                    "parent": "63",
                    "text": "- Focos contiguos (sinusitis, otitis): ~50%",
                    "guid": "PerSpjRFvnpqU9GiVek1Gg",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "65",
                    "parent": "63",
                    "text": "- Hematógeno (endocarditis): 25%",
                    "guid": "DEF142iQKNZrKsPhQqno5A",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "66",
                    "parent": "63",
                    "text": "- Criptogénico (probablemente odontógeno): 15%",
                    "guid": "JFY9DwRbNyIA-vAYaxS7cw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "67",
                    "parent": "63",
                    "text": "- Neurocirugía/traumatismo: 10%",
                    "guid": "VOsbkwK6-Q12xTWOJdH8Sw",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "68",
                "parent": "60",
                "text": "- Patógenos: estreptococos anaerobios/aerobios, microaerófilos, Enterobacteriaceae",
                "guid": "QhhckiKeAVkJKfPyf2RUIw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "69",
                "parent": "60",
                "text": "- Tratamiento: determinado por proceso predisponente más probable",
                "guid": "cPA0uEB42fdvX5abKVi1EQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "70",
                "parent": "60",
                "text": "- Aspiración quirúrgica indicada para abscesos grandes (>2,5 cm)",
                "guid": "LoE7cXR_dGtKTY3qbGwOGA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "71",
                "parent": "60",
                "text": "- Duración antibiótica: mínimo 4-6 semanas",
                "guid": "KMUy5TShX4xCVUMyNQaoyA",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "72",
            "parent": "59",
            "text": "### Abscesos\nepidurales espinales",
            "guid": "HTGIYi2ABxN3sJGsQYfFcQ",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "73",
                "parent": "72",
                "text": "- Causa principal: diseminación hematógena",
                "guid": "Mds-NXirgcUsnIDlBsZZyA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "74",
                "parent": "72",
                "text": "- Patógenos principales: S. aureus (50%), estreptococos, gramnegativos",
                "guid": "e2Z60iNhtnMsmFYTO6d_Kg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "75",
                "parent": "72",
                "text": "- Factores predisponentes: endocarditis, drogas IV, catéteres a largo plazo",
                "guid": "XBh572PEWkhjQPWBHjDWgg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "76",
                "parent": "72",
                "text": "- Síntomas: dolor localizado que se irradia",
                "guid": "BmJbomxq6XMdlSqld1KQWg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "77",
                "parent": "72",
                "text": "- Diagnóstico: resonancia magnética (modalidad de elección)",
                "guid": "LOPDagz0wUEgq0VrW2T-3A",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "78",
                "parent": "72",
                "text": "- Manejo: obtener cultivos sanguíneos antes de iniciar antibióticos",
                "guid": "AXQ1rGr401VH0Qz0KjlokQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "79",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "## Encefalitis",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "80",
            "parent": "79",
            "text": "- Inflamación del parénquima cerebral",
            "guid": "H5oy4QomUCZfQBFZPMu7RA",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "81",
            "parent": "79",
            "text": "- Criterio mayor: alteración de conciencia >24 h",
            "guid": "N6ZXOVbwowZ-U4C1aYGVbg",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "82",
            "parent": "79",
            "text": "- Criterios menores: fiebre, convulsiones, hallazgos neurológicos focales",
            "guid": "T5wkyyrwAZpwR-82SwKfnQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "83",
            "parent": "79",
            "text": "- Agente causal desconocido en 37-70% de casos",
            "guid": "TlG4DhzgRUkGqh7HKmox_Q",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "84",
            "parent": "79",
            "text": "- Causas comunes: enfermedades virales y autoinmunes",
            "guid": "AKSfkmnrFEhImwh_Bwb7NA",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "85",
            "parent": "79",
            "text": "### Encefalitis viral",
            "guid": "VlX9u2YwMyV-WYuOAznBJg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "86",
                "parent": "85",
                "text": "- VHS-1: causa más común de\nencefalitis esporádica en EEUU",
                "guid": "cyT0Zh8E0PpensACdJkqEg",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "87",
                    "parent": "86",
                    "text": "- Presentación: fiebre, convulsiones, alteración mental, déficits neurológicos",
                    "guid": "Cf2kTyZvzPYe0pKjKZfXMQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "88",
                    "parent": "86",
                    "text": "- Diagnóstico: PCR en LCR (sensibilidad 98%, especificidad 94%)",
                    "guid": "MJYdHH4So_xmY5J1aDx0VQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "89",
                    "parent": "86",
                    "text": "- Tratamiento: aciclovir IV inmediato (14-21 días)",
                    "guid": "VQNHAmS3EypRvgnDJJ9rzQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "90",
                    "parent": "86",
                    "text": "- Factores de mal pronóstico: edad avanzada, escala Glasgow baja, retraso terapia",
                    "guid": "D6cUxUIF-PlvogtqXfjM0w",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "91",
                "parent": "85",
                "text": "- VVZ: causa tratable y\nfrecuentemente infradiagnosticada",
                "guid": "XuY-QnZMKjIIYv7QX4rd1A",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "92",
                    "parent": "91",
                    "text": "- Puede presentarse sin exantema vesicular",
                    "guid": "YDc-elD-B1BmkdkINo08Ng",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "93",
                    "parent": "91",
                    "text": "- Tratamiento: aciclovir IV (10-14 días)",
                    "guid": "Ny46dWTrZJc5xv1cKlMu2w",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "94",
                "parent": "85",
                "text": "- Arbovirus",
                "guid": "A_A1kRhlvV4e7FjtDe3Z4A",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "95",
                    "parent": "94",
                    "text": "- Más frecuentes en verano/otoño en EEUU",
                    "guid": "PtWKVD2-65A3hbERb2uncA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "96",
                    "parent": "94",
                    "text": "- Incluyen: VNO, encefalitis equina oriental/occidental, virus de la Crosse",
                    "guid": "O9GPjB3pQ4ZXqBvFENTWjw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "97",
                    "parent": "94",
                    "text": "- VNO: causa más común de encefalitis viral epidémica en EEUU",
                    "guid": "AqBWsSlmJYg1dEJcEkdrdg",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "98",
                    "parent": "94",
                    "text": "- Síntomas: meningitis, encefalitis, parálisis flácida, temblores faciales",
                    "guid": "a2wegSUWTcdwQDhJSlJcww",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "99",
                    "parent": "94",
                    "text": "- Diagnóstico: PCR en LCR o suero",
                    "guid": "G2J3-XijNxkp3TqYe5m2cw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "100",
                    "parent": "94",
                    "text": "- Tratamiento: medidas de apoyo",
                    "guid": "SaE-aRBvE6AyJvKpAM943g",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "101",
                "parent": "85",
                "text": "- VIH: causa demencia\nasociada en etapas tardías",
                "guid": "dVp4N2vt8AUrIqe5eUqtyA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "102",
                    "parent": "101",
                    "text": "- También como encefalitis CD8,\ninfiltración linfocitos CD8+",
                    "guid": "BFOtY0oPAKYHOIepQyk3tw",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "103",
            "parent": "79",
            "text": "### Encefalitis\nautoinmune",
            "guid": "B83sNj6-OLoylN8nQ597ww",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "104",
                "parent": "103",
                "text": "- Anti-receptor NMDA: más común",
                "guid": "XKd8QQo8-uxUdFJSX0fS8g",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "105",
                "parent": "103",
                "text": "- Inicialmente síndrome paraneoplásico (teratomas ováricos)",
                "guid": "M6MgdAnolK5xjz5oHw8-9Q",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "106",
                "parent": "103",
                "text": "- Después de fase prodrómica: cambios comportamiento, psicosis, convulsiones",
                "guid": "Lv7idWHPdrFpYZu5SmFabg",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "107",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "# Enfermedades priónicas del\nsistema nervioso central",
        "guid": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "108",
            "parent": "107",
            "text": "## Características\ngenerales",
            "guid": "WnKtyhM-1lFF-xDiJBPsNA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "109",
                "parent": "108",
                "text": "- Causadas por proteína priónica plegada anormalmente",
                "guid": "I63p8XgiA4sk42USGQhiKQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "110",
                "parent": "108",
                "text": "- Enfermedades neurodegenerativas raras pero inexorablemente progresivas",
                "guid": "ZA_zkVAGDMwSUw_xaGOg9A",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "111",
                "parent": "108",
                "text": "- Rápidamente mortales",
                "guid": "GhUNchmLl5orjNisIeL5qQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "112",
                "parent": "108",
                "text": "- Caracterizadas por demencia y ataxia",
                "guid": "WEnQVV4ht9NlgnVsNPFMlg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "113",
                "parent": "108",
                "text": "- Mecanismos\nde desarrollo:",
                "guid": "N7GENAM6qjJmHm6fW19uJQ",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "114",
                    "parent": "113",
                    "text": "- Esporádicas (espontáneas)",
                    "guid": "aF6ywDn2x74UOR-IHAHTNA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "115",
                    "parent": "113",
                    "text": "- Familiares (genéticas)",
                    "guid": "Q99cbAXIXfA7ERIqct4-4g",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "116",
                    "parent": "113",
                    "text": "- Adquiridas (infecciosas o transmisibles)",
                    "guid": "Z5fUoSRyreM9P5lQQgqCaw",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "117",
                "parent": "108",
                "text": "- Diagnóstico: considerar en pacientes con demencia y ataxia rápidamente progresivas",
                "guid": "e1ytvgsB07J0Z9BOX2yhTw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "118",
                "parent": "108",
                "text": "- No existe tratamiento conocido",
                "guid": "Wwfgfga64EBH0EJDdRzt8A",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "119",
            "parent": "107",
            "text": "## Enfermedad de\nCreutzfeldt-Jakob esporádica",
            "guid": "IEZ32nNdGu8W_-eZeJBILw",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "120",
                "parent": "119",
                "text": "- Forma más común de ECJ",
                "guid": "UX7Sw3yCXQUtgZTFOd2Fgw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "121",
                "parent": "119",
                "text": "- Incidencia: uno por millón de individuos a nivel mundial",
                "guid": "Nnkkw0G6tE1V31i3eliBMA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "122",
                "parent": "119",
                "text": "- No se conocen factores de riesgo ambientales",
                "guid": "R4MSPRDwauFtNsASLxrm3g",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "123",
                "parent": "119",
                "text": "- Manifestaciones\nclínicas:",
                "guid": "Q6ev1UlqYaNcbXu2FSaCmA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "124",
                    "parent": "123",
                    "text": "- Demencia rápidamente progresiva",
                    "guid": "NWMYxCp2WWJxJWlKbRSc-A",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "125",
                    "parent": "123",
                    "text": "- Curso típico: 4-6 meses",
                    "guid": "LbEDlVdD1-lIdAseKQ2xUw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "126",
                    "parent": "123",
                    "text": "- Ataxia, mioclonía, signos piramidales y extrapiramidales",
                    "guid": "YkWrmzzb22wIelKiPU2MGQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "127",
                    "parent": "123",
                    "text": "- No es frecuente la pérdida de visión",
                    "guid": "Q5a7rFBKlOUyanoKY90zhw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "128",
                    "parent": "123",
                    "text": "- Pacientes entran en coma antes de fallecer",
                    "guid": "Rey-qQnvEHxPBAgbfGXjbA",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "129",
                "parent": "119",
                "text": "- Diagnóstico:",
                "guid": "S6nEySTjYNJ2vmScEyzXBw",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "130",
                    "parent": "129",
                    "text": "- Anamnesis clínica y RM",
                    "guid": "NdPLtGP1JK5CR73lazbkeA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "131",
                    "parent": "129",
                    "text": "- Análisis positivo para proteínas tau total o 14-3-3",
                    "guid": "Dmt-ETNtJy9YS4FxPByBpg",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "132",
            "parent": "107",
            "text": "## Enfermedades\npriónicas transmisibles",
            "guid": "CrD_GSC_jI9lKjL5bPaqtA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "133",
                "parent": "132",
                "text": "- ECJ variante (vECJ): forma humana de\nencefalopatía espongiforme bovina",
                "guid": "XZtn-22khZsqRDbOITIjqA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "134",
                    "parent": "133",
                    "text": "- Afecta generalmente a personas jóvenes (15-50 años)",
                    "guid": "Pe8agFyusNgFD1cvAZbKVQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "135",
                    "parent": "133",
                    "text": "- Manifestaciones neuropsiquiátricas rápidamente progresivas",
                    "guid": "JhkSe2F80uUWvUztbAXRJA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "136",
                    "parent": "133",
                    "text": "- Síntomas: depresión, introversión, neuropatía periférica",
                    "guid": "a2vjYWXBVQhoa7SRNxWoKw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "137",
                    "parent": "133",
                    "text": "- Seguidos por ataxia cerebelosa, movimientos involuntarios, declive cognitivo",
                    "guid": "CqS1218qGS1KQn8yQHiBjw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "138",
                    "parent": "133",
                    "text": "- Periodo de evolución: 12 meses",
                    "guid": "Qx893AyKPRcrr2YHUYq77Q",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "139",
                    "parent": "133",
                    "text": "- Transmisible por productos sanguíneos y tejidos",
                    "guid": "P_dkRwP653gNpz2TSqhjYA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "140",
                    "parent": "133",
                    "text": "- Problema grave de salud pública mundial",
                    "guid": "JLp0B3LRcIw3nw4UAlXcAw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "141",
                    "parent": "133",
                    "text": "- Diagnóstico: hallazgos típicos en RM (signo del \"palo de hockey\" en tálamo posterior)",
                    "guid": "YHX2J2HjROIjh_-rHmUQpw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "142",
                    "parent": "133",
                    "text": "- Biopsia amigdalina para detectar proteína priónica asociada",
                    "guid": "PpH1uiiXVtof-9r9ZKsINg",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "143",
                "parent": "132",
                "text": "- ECJ iatrogénica:\nextremadamente rara",
                "guid": "VI7xajablJlGkwh4bNWYgw",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "144",
                    "parent": "143",
                    "text": "- Documentada\ntransmisión por:",
                    "guid": "AvlYtxtyY34KBd9NH3PVqg",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "145",
                        "parent": "144",
                        "text": "- Hormona del crecimiento y gonadotropina derivadas de hipófisis de cadáver",
                        "guid": "ChQpvza5J-pQsNladYANIQ",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "146",
                        "parent": "144",
                        "text": "- Duramadre",
                        "guid": "HHp88zkcjesslbVMJx8yzg",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "147",
                        "parent": "144",
                        "text": "- Agujas de electroencefalografía estereotácticas",
                        "guid": "GEanGXbYNH5nl7RdW2Xk9Q",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "148",
                        "parent": "144",
                        "text": "- Instrumentos neuroquirúrgicos",
                        "guid": "A2JxlRNHGmQs8KDiQ1nV3A",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "149",
                        "parent": "144",
                        "text": "- Trasplantes corneales",
                        "guid": "F0IB3TqX3nUOAjk8O_x15A",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "150",
                        "parent": "144",
                        "text": "- Instrumental médico",
                        "guid": "LWlPAUWhR1E-UlHnDd9FKA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "151",
                        "parent": "144",
                        "text": "- Electrodos de EEG implantados",
                        "guid": "J4SMM2HaUZIsRFXPZhaB7g",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "152",
                        "parent": "144",
                        "text": "- Transfusiones sanguíneas",
                        "guid": "CnGobExAMMxKwYokFIXSLA",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "153",
            "parent": "107",
            "text": "## Enfermedades\npriónicas familiares",
            "guid": "NNzydRdQ5sdVbp84P06a4Q",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "154",
                "parent": "153",
                "text": "- Asociadas a mutaciones en genes de proteínas priónicas",
                "guid": "LXPJFy4qvNVIO314MNY6rA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "155",
                "parent": "153",
                "text": "- Incluyen:",
                "guid": "R9ORFlMCoOJrDJD4b1gdSg",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "156",
                    "parent": "155",
                    "text": "- Síndrome de Gerstmann-Sträussler-Scheinker: gravemente progresivo",
                    "guid": "QXHXOXUsHlp0MBCJWLPZFg",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "157",
                    "parent": "155",
                    "text": "- Insomnio familiar fatal: rápidamente progresivo",
                    "guid": "L8P8zwIyScUUsE77XS1L0A",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "158",
            "parent": "107",
            "text": "## Criterios diagnósticos",
            "guid": "BeCUZneHYvEyaZ9_SFjp8Q",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "159",
                "parent": "158",
                "text": "### Universidad de California,\nSan Francisco (2007)",
                "guid": "Y5EXlCAwKVxT1G0NZopwSw",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "160",
                    "parent": "159",
                    "text": "- Declive cognitivo rápido",
                    "guid": "O6KM2l3aTFoF_kX1EDF-RA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "161",
                    "parent": "159",
                    "text": "- Dos o más de los\nsiguientes signos/síntomas:",
                    "guid": "Im7yLhnXQMxhwMEZNuTTIQ",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "162",
                        "parent": "161",
                        "text": "- Mioclonía",
                        "guid": "FHXg80yRTm19BxbHQemqCg",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "163",
                        "parent": "161",
                        "text": "- Disfunción piramidal/extrapiramidal",
                        "guid": "erwLQkVClD9yv-S3PC3iew",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "164",
                        "parent": "161",
                        "text": "- Disfunción visual",
                        "guid": "Om6ymWbv9UAU4buSajKvaA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "165",
                        "parent": "161",
                        "text": "- Disfunción cerebelosa",
                        "guid": "aSI_BSmSCo1HX_s4MPXQHA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "166",
                        "parent": "161",
                        "text": "- Mutismo acinético",
                        "guid": "fJSrbzJsjDAgTe1mMXGd5A",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "167",
                        "parent": "161",
                        "text": "- Signos corticales focales",
                        "guid": "Sb1y-HW8jJ5wwDjGLU6KjA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "168",
                        "parent": "161",
                        "text": "- EEG y/o RM típicas",
                        "guid": "Fey1-kSUpdMT2PrXUY9C1A",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "169",
                "parent": "158",
                "text": "### European MRI-CJD\nConsortium (2009)",
                "guid": "ZmiPOV7H1-B4zn0sYSSaew",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "170",
                    "parent": "169",
                    "text": "- Demencia progresiva",
                    "guid": "JApsIGuOYeMdUnz2XnkeuQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "171",
                    "parent": "169",
                    "text": "- Uno de los siguientes\nsignos o síntomas:",
                    "guid": "fNIPYUwUNVwtKPzqT1BmhA",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "172",
                        "parent": "171",
                        "text": "- Mioclonía",
                        "guid": "Un5XIzI0OIhIq84iO6CWKA",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "173",
                        "parent": "171",
                        "text": "- Síntomas\npiramidales/extrapiramidales",
                        "guid": "W8ZDFRALyVpslmZEWFruhQ",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "174",
                        "parent": "171",
                        "text": "- Disfunción\nvisual/cerebelosa",
                        "guid": "QnhViwzkU6oJzIxpDDXIgw",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "175",
                        "parent": "171",
                        "text": "- Mutismo acinético",
                        "guid": "AqDgSHqMxS85hFMPGI2WQg",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "176",
                    "parent": "169",
                    "text": "- Cualquiera de:",
                    "guid": "fkht5XXUywwK8PytWg6w-g",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "id": "177",
                        "parent": "176",
                        "text": "- EEG típica",
                        "guid": "PyFrA01dTeZqHNkXYZBdMQ",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "178",
                        "parent": "176",
                        "text": "- Elevación de proteína 14-3-3 en LCR (con duración total de enfermedad <2 años)",
                        "guid": "ZzSOskvdmjAYdTBSTZ0d6w",
                        "children": []
                      },
                      {
                        "id": "179",
                        "parent": "176",
                        "text": "- RM típica",
                        "guid": "KqVyEBFDrX4uwbhmTq_eMA",
                        "children": []
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "180",
            "parent": "107",
            "text": "## Puntos clave",
            "guid": "W3BTaQm3Bj5XdLlMQqTiGw",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "181",
                "parent": "180",
                "text": "- Las enfermedades priónicas deben incluirse en el diagnóstico diferencial de pacientes con demencia y ataxia rápidamente progresivas no explicadas",
                "guid": "BGu2nDw2K-lUjrJ0BwyW5A",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "182",
                "parent": "180",
                "text": "- La enfermedad de Creutzfeldt-Jakob esporádica es la forma más común de enfermedad priónica y no tiene factores de riesgo conocidos",
                "guid": "NsLxGA4TBYMfmi0ndeRcGw",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
